        "text_HyjmeA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p>At Allen, cycling has always been about more than equipment. It’s about movement, curiosity, and the simple satisfaction of getting out the door and onto the bike. In 2026, we’re formalizing that idea with a new monthly feature: <strong>Where We’re Riding</strong>.</p><p>Each month, we’ll highlight a small selection of cycling events and ride destinations around the world—spanning gravel, road, and mountain biking. Some will be marquee events. Others will simply be places worth riding, whether or not an event is happening. Participation is optional. Inspiration is the point.</p><p>This series isn’t about results, rankings, or start times. It’s about giving yourself a reason to ride—something to plan for, look forward to, or draw ideas from as the year unfolds.</p>"
