        "text_jcmrz6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p>The purpose of <strong>Where We’re Riding</strong> isn’t to create obligation. It’s to create <strong>permission</strong>—permission to plan a trip, sign up for something new, or simply ride somewhere different than usual.</p><p>You don’t need to travel far.<br/>You don’t need to race.<br/>You just need one ride that gives the year a starting point.</p><p>We’ll be adding a new installment each month in 2026, following destinations and events across Europe, the U.S., and beyond. Some months will lean adventurous, others reflective. All of them are meant to encourage time on the bike.</p>"
